  "title": "feat(bem): Make the searchBox BEMish",
  "body": "I've also updated the `poweredBy` as well. I've changed the logic of\nadding inline `style` to using a specific class (defined in the\ndefault `css` file). I've switched the display/hide logic. We no\nlonger need to define a `display=true` in the props to show it, but\na `hidden=true` to hide it instead.\n\nBREAKING CHANGE: The `poweredBy` component now expect a `hidden=false`\nto be hidden, instead of a `display=true` to be displayed.\n",
